# Agra Local Guide - Context File

## City Overview
Agra is a historic city in Uttar Pradesh, India, famous for the Taj Mahal and Mughal architecture.

## Local Food Culture
- **Petha**: Famous sweet made from ash gourd. Best shops: Panchhi Petha, Bhimsain Devidayal
- **Breakfast Specials**: Bedai-Jalebi at Deviram Sweets, Kachori at Ram Babu Paranthe Wale
- **Street Food**: Dalmoth (spicy namkeen), Chaat at Sadar Bazaar
- **Mughlai Cuisine**: Pinch of Spice, Joney's Place

## Local Slang & Phrases
- "Bhaiya/Didi" - Respectful way to address people
- "Thoda adjust karo" - Please adjust/make space
- "Sahi hai" - That's good/okay
- "Chalega" - It will work/okay

