## Tourist Hotspots
- **Taj Mahal**: Visit at sunrise (6-7 AM) for fewer crowds
- **Agra Fort**: 2-3 hours needed
- **Fatehpur Sikri**: 40km away, half-day trip
- **Hidden Gems**: Mehtab Bagh (sunset Taj view), Sikandra, Itmad-ud-Daulah

## Shopping Markets
- **Sadar Bazaar**: Leather goods, shoes
- **Kinari Bazaar**: Jewelry, traditional items
- **Shah Market**: Street food hub

## Best Time to Visit
October to March (pleasant weather). Avoid summers (April-June) - too hot!

## Local Etiquette
- Remove shoes at religious sites
- Dress modestly at monuments
- Bargain politely at markets
- Respect local customs
